第二級毒品者，處3年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NTDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c389%2c20221130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NTDM,111,訴,389,20221130,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"389","JDATE":"20221130","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}